title: El Dewrito Halo Online Multi
description:
Eldewrito is a project focused on multiplayer, contrast to Eldorito's focus on singleplayer. It comprises a launcher which automatically updates executable and data files as needed for the latest Eldewrito features, and verifies these files to ensure all people are playing on the same version (This could also be seen as basic anti-cheat measures).

As of version 0.4.5, Eldewrito unlocks Local Area Network play which can be used alongside virtual network gaming clients like Evolve or the custom built OracleNet to play online with others.

====================================================================================
This is a release of El Dewrito only, not Halo Online itself.
